    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/73f0724d2dae211d43a8bb57ec9aabe4.poster.avif?t=1739882638\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/73f0724d2dae211d43a8bb57ec9aabe4.webm?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/73f0724d2dae211d43a8bb57ec9aabe4.mp4?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Photo-Toy Ocean</strong> is a desktop background toy where you<strong> take pictures of underwater sea life</strong>. <br>Running at a <strong>320x320</strong> windowed resolution, players will let the simple simulation play out only occasionally dropping in to snap a rare fish or maybe even grab some trash.<br><br>Photo-Toy Ocean is meant to be a non-intrusive experience and played passively in the background as you do other tasks in your life.<br><br><br><br><br>Snap photos of interesting fish, rays and other sea life!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/7f3ea0fd1fcf64f2a422509c319bbaaf.poster.avif?t=1739882638\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/7f3ea0fd1fcf64f2a422509c319bbaaf.webm?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/7f3ea0fd1fcf64f2a422509c319bbaaf.mp4?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Complete a photo album of all the creatures you encounter!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0f8c9eab1a86d2e0213500033a2d5816.poster.avif?t=1739882638\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0f8c9eab1a86d2e0213500033a2d5816.webm?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0f8c9eab1a86d2e0213500033a2d5816.mp4?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Clear the ocean of the occasional trash you see!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0144a925ac7b966be569344823e14efc.poster.avif?t=1739882638\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0144a925ac7b966be569344823e14efc.webm?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/0144a925ac7b966be569344823e14efc.mp4?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Keep an eye out for rare sights!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/46d6cb19d0a3d465cf86837a8d7fee27.poster.avif?t=1739882638\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/46d6cb19d0a3d465cf86837a8d7fee27.webm?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145860/extras/46d6cb19d0a3d465cf86837a8d7fee27.mp4?t=1739882638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as you work!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app